Class NativeType

java.lang.Object
  com.google.gxp.compiler.base.SerializableAbstractNode

All Implemented Interfaces:
Node, Serializable
public class NativeType
extends Type

Native types are essentially black-boxes as far as GXP is concerned. The output language is responsible for doing whatever type checking it can with these.

See Also:
